<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<root>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .invoice {
            font-family: inherit;
            font-weight: 100;
            width: 95%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 2% auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 70px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #fff;
            min-height: auto;
            font-size: 13;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;

            align-items: center;
        }

        .header--invoice {
            order: 2;
            text-align: right;
            width: 40%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .invoice--date,
        .invoice--number {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #494949;
        }

        .invoice--recipient {
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .header--logo {
            order: 1;
            font-size: 30px;
            width: 60%;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .logo--address {
            font-size: 13px;
            padding: 4px;

            width: 50%;
        }

        .logo--address1 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: lato;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .description {
            margin: auto;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .sessiontitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: initial;
            padding: 1px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-transform: capitalize;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .spansubtitle {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .bottomcls {
            position: relative;
            top: -18px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-family: serif;
            color: #795548;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
#set ($customerDetails = $email.dataForPdf.get("customerDetails").get(0)) #set ($customerUnitDetails = $email.dataForPdf.get("customerUnitDetails").get(0)) #set ($info = ${email.demandNoteGeneratorInfo})
<article class="invoice" style="font-family: Times New Roman, Times, sans-serif;">
    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;"><b> Date:${customerDetails.get("todayDate")} </b></p>

     <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: left;">
        To, <br />
        <b> M/S. BAJAJ HOUSING FINANCE LTD.</b><br />
        4th Floor, Bajaj Finserv Corporate Office,<br />
        Off Pune-Ahmednagar Road, Viman Nagar, Pune-411 014.
    </p>


    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
       <b> Subject:</b> Issue of NOC-cum-Release letter of <b> Flat NO. ${customerDetails.get("flatName")} </b> in <b>'${customerDetails.get("blockName")}'</b> of Building known as <b>'${customerDetails.get("siteName")}' </b> situated at Sy No:47/1,
        47/2A, 47/2B, 47/3, 48/3 &amp; 48/4 Whitefield Village, K.R.Puram Hobli, Bangalore East Taluk, Bangalore-560 066.
    </p>
    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
        <b> Ref. No.: 1. Bajaj Housing Finance Sanction Letter dated 22-Sept-2022 </b>
    </p>
    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
        Respected Sir / Madam,
    </p>
    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
        &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; We have sold the following Flat and you are requested to give the <u>NOC-cum-Release letter</u> for the said unit at the earliest.
    </p>
    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
        &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The Purchaser/s has taken loan from ${customerUnitDetails.get("customerLoanBank")} and their disbursement is pending. Hence you are requested to issue the <u>NOC-cum-release letter</u> at the earliest
    </p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid black; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 20px;">
         <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
          <th colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;background-color:#87CEEB;text-align: center;"> Details of Purchaser</th>
            
        </tr>
        
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Purchaser's Full Name
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
               <b>  ${customerDetails.get("customerNames")} </b>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Purchaser's Mobile No.
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerDetails.get("custBookInfoPhoneNo")}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Flat no
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                <b> ${customerDetails.get("flatName")} </b>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Wing
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerDetails.get("blockName")}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Floor
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                <b> ${customerDetails.get("floorName")} </b>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Area (in Sqft)
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerUnitDetails.get("SBUA Sq.ft")}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px; width: 50%;">
                Project Name
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px; width: 50%;">
                ${customerDetails.get("siteName")}
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Project Location/ Address
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Whitefield Village, K.R.Puram Hobli, Bangalore
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Consideration/ Agreement value (in Rs.)
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerDetails.get("totalSaleConsideration")}/-
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Loan Amount (in Rs.)
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                <b> Lender’s Name </b>
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                <b>${customerUnitDetails.get("customerLoanBank")}</b>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Own contribution given to us (in Rs.)
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerDetails.get("strtotalMilestonePaidAmount")}/-
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
               Booking date
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                ${customerDetails.get("bookingDateSlashFormat")}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border: 1px solid black;">
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
                Agreement for sale date
            </td>
            <td style="border: 1px solid black; text-align: left; padding: 8px;">
             ${customerUnitDetails.get("agreementDate")}
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <br />
    <p contenteditable="true" style="margin-top: 12px;">Kindly do the needful at the earliest.</p>

    <p contenteditable="true" style="text-align: justify;">
        Thanking you in anticipation.<br />
        Yours faithfully,  <br /> 
     <b> FOR SUMADHURA INFRACON PVT LTD</b>
    </p>
</article>
</body>
</root>